data.description: ***Assumable VA loan available to buyer - 30 year fixed at 4.75% - $529,000 remaining on loan - buyer DOES NOT have to be active-duty military or a veteran to assume this loan***Stunning home in Riverchase Subdivision! This warm and inviting neighborhood offers all the expectations and benefits of a well-kept community, including underground utilities, without the monthly HOA. Total serenity, yet in proximity to all shopping conveniences, schools, medical and more.This 4 bed 3 1/2 bath home with an office leaves nothing to be desired. 10-ft ceilings throughout. The kitchen featuring abundant cabinet space, an island, double oven, and walk-in pantry is a chef's dream!The master suite boasts a large walk-in closet with built in safe, double vanity in bathroom, and walk-in tile shower. Enjoy breakfast, lunch, or dinner in the sunroom overlooking seemingly endless views of woods. The large fenced in backyard is perfect for children, pets, and entertaining.The additional 572 square feet of living space above the garage, with separate entrance, provides the unique opportunity for an Airbnb or in-law suite.Other home features include whole house generator, new HVAC (2022), encapsulated crawl space with dehumidifier, mini-split in living space above garage, and security system. Current owner upgrades include the following: opened living room area continued Berkshire Hickory tile, installed top quality LVP in lieu of carpeting in main level bedrooms, office and living room professionally painted, new Whirlpool refrigerator, installed an EV CCS fast charging station in garage, installed dog run adjacent to back porch, and opened up back porch, added 2nd set of stairs, and recently stained. Schedule your showing today as this beautiful home won't last long!*Buyer to verify all information before making an informed offer*
